。","account.signInTitleDefault":"登录后继续制作。","account.signInBodyCheckout":"你的通行证属于在这里登录的 Flowers 账户。确认后，我们会把你带回礼物工作室。","account.signInBodyDefault":"你的花束、卡片和礼物链接会绑定到 Flowers 账户，所以从这里开始的作品也能在 app 里继续。","account.benefitAttach":"把结账绑定到账户","account.benefitUnlock":"解锁礼物工作室","account.benefitReturnCheckout":"返回结账","account.benefitSave":"保存每一束花","account.benefitSync":"与 Flowers 同步","account.benefitReturnDraft":"返回草稿","account.syncedBouquets":"已同步花束","account.manageSubscription":"取消或管理订阅","account.providerBillingBody":"可管理 checkout provider 账单或随时取消。访问权限会持续到 {{date}}。","account.openingProvider":"正在打开 checkout provider...","account.manageProvider":"在 checkout provider 中取消 / 管理","account.mobileBillingBody":"此 Blooming 访问权限来自移动端。请从购买它的商店账户取消。","account.mobileLinksAria":"移动端订阅链接","account.cancelAppStore":"在 App Store 中取消","account.cancelGooglePlay":"在 Google Play 中取消","account.benefitsAria":"登录后可启用的功能","account.embeddedTitle":"请先在 Chrome 或 Safari 中打开。","account.embeddedBody":"Google 会阻止 Instagram、Facebook、Messenger 和其他应用内浏览器中的登录。","account.openBrowser":"在浏览器中打开","account.consentPrefix":"我同意","account.terms":"使用条款","account.consentMiddle":"和","account.privacy":"隐私政策","account.consentSuffix":"，并理解 Flowers 会为账户登录、结账、安全和礼物发送使用必要 cookie 与本地存储。","account.optionalConsentBefore":"可选分析和营销会保持关闭，除非你在这里选择开启:","account.optionalConsentSuffix":"。","account.openingGoogle":"正在打开 Google...","account.continueGoogle":"继续使用 Google","account.openingApple":"正在打开 Apple...","account.continueApple":"继续使用 Apple","account.authNoteEmbedded":"在真正的浏览器中打开后，登录并返回你的草稿。","account.authNoteDefault":"在手机上，登录会在此标签页继续，批准后会返回这里。"}),Object.assign(H.en,{"meta.title":"Flowers — Compose a Bouquet","meta.description":"Compose and send private flower gifts from the Flowers web studio."}),Object.assign(H.es,{"meta.title":"Flowers — Componer un ramo","meta.description":"Crea y envía regalos florales privados desde el estudio web de Flowers."}),Object.assign(H.id,{"meta.title":"Flowers — Rangkai Buket","meta.description":"Rangkai d