.loadingRecorder":"Loading camera and hand tracking…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Start recording","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Record again","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Stop recording","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Camera ready","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Load camera to preview","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Before you record","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Open on a tablet or laptop","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"Hand recording uses your camera, real-time hand tracking, and a live flower trail. It needs a larger screen in landscape and more processing power than most phones provide.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Turn your device sideways (landscape)","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Load camera & hand tracking","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"Record up to 15 seconds","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"On a tablet or laptop in landscape, load the camera to preview and record.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Load the camera when you are ready to record."},es:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"Gira el dispositivo. La grabación con las manos solo funciona en horizontal en una tablet o portátil.","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"La grabación con las manos es para tablets y portátiles. La cámara, el seguimiento de manos y el rastro de flores necesitan una pantalla más grande y más potencia que la de la mayoría de los móviles.","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"Horizontal obligatorio","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"Tablet o portátil","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"Iniciando cámara…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"Tablet o portátil · horizontal","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"Video de creación listo","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"Graba tu creación primero","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"Cargar cámara y seguimiento de manos","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"Cargar cámara","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"Cargando cámara y seguimiento de manos…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Empezar grabación","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Grabar de nuevo","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Detener grabación","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Cámara lista","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Carga la cámara para previsualizar","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Antes de grabar","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Ábrelo en una tablet o portátil","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"La grabación con las manos usa tu cámara, seguimiento de manos en tiempo real y un rastro de flores en vivo. Necesita una pantalla más grande en horizontal y más potencia que la mayoría de los móviles.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Gira el dispositivo (horizontal)","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Carga cámara y seguimiento de manos","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"Graba hasta 15 segundos","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"En una tablet o portátil en horizontal, carga la cámara para previsualizar y grabar.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Carga la cámara cuando estés listo para grabar."},id:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"Putar perangkat ke posisi landscape. Rekaman tangan hanya berfungsi dalam landscape di tablet atau laptop.","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"Rekaman tangan untuk tablet dan laptop. Kamera, pelacakan tangan, dan jejak bunga membutuhkan layar lebih besar dan daya pemrosesan lebih kuat daripada kebanyakan ponsel.","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"Landscape wajib","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"Tablet atau laptop","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"Memulai kamera…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"Tablet atau laptop · landscape","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"Video kreasi siap","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"Rekam kreasi Anda dulu","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"Muat kamera & pelacakan tangan","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"Muat kamera","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"Memuat kamera dan pelacakan tangan…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Mulai merekam","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Rekam lagi","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Berhenti merekam","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Kamera siap","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Muat kamera untuk pratinjau","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Sebelum merekam","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Buka di tablet atau laptop","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"Rekaman tangan memakai kamera, pelacakan tangan real-time, dan jejak bunga langsung. Butuh layar lebih besar dalam landscape dan daya pemrosesan lebih kuat daripada kebanyakan ponsel.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Putar perangkat ke landscape","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Muat kamera & pelacakan tangan","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"Rekam hingga 15 detik","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"Di tablet atau laptop dalam landscape, muat kamera untuk pratinjau dan rekam.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Muat kamera saat Anda siap merekam."},ja:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"端末を横向きにしてください。手の録画は、タブレットまたはノートパソコンでの横向き表示のみ利用できます。","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"手の録画はタブレットとノートパソコン向けです。カメラ、手の追跡、花の軌跡には、多くのスマートフォンより大きな画面と処理能力が必要です。","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"横向きが必要です","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"タブレットまたはPC","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"カメラを起動中…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"タブレットまたはPC · 横向き","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"作成動画の準備完了","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"まず作成動画を録画してください","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"カメラと手の追跡を読み込む","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"カメラを読み込む","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"カメラと手の追跡を読み込み中…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"録画を開始","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"もう一度録画","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"録画を停止","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"カメラ準備完了","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"プレビューするにはカメラを読み込んでください","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"録画の前に","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"タブレットまたはノートパソコンで開いてください","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"手の録画はカメラ、リアルタイムの手の追跡、ライブの花の軌跡を使います。横向きの大きな画面と、多くのスマートフォンより強い処理能力が必要です。","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"端末を横向きにする","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"カメラと手の追跡を読み込む","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"最大15秒まで録画する","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"タブレットまたはノートパソコンを横向きにしてから、カメラを読み込んでプレビューと録画を始めてください。","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"録画の準備ができたらカメラを読み込んでください。"},ms:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"Pusingkan peranti ke landskap. Rakaman tangan hanya berfungsi dalam landskap pada tablet atau komputer riba.","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"Rakaman tangan untuk tablet dan komputer riba. Kamera, penjejakan tangan, dan jejak bunga memerlukan skrin lebih besar dan kuasa pemprosesan lebih tinggi daripada kebanyakan telefon.","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"Landskap diperlukan","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"Tablet atau komputer riba","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"Memulakan kamera…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"Tablet atau komputer riba · landskap","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"Video ciptaan sedia","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"Rakam ciptaan anda dahulu","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"Muat kamera & penjejakan tangan","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"Muat kamera","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"Memuatkan kamera dan penjejakan tangan…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Mula merakam","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Rakam semula","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Hentikan rakaman","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Kamera sedia","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Muat kamera untuk pratonton","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Sebelum merakam","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Buka pada tablet atau komputer riba","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"Rakaman tangan menggunakan kamera, penjejakan tangan masa nyata, dan jejak bunga langsung. Ia memerlukan skrin lebih besar dalam landskap dan kuasa pemprosesan lebih tinggi daripada kebanyakan telefon.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Putar peranti ke landskap","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Muat kamera & penjejakan tangan","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"Rakam sehingga 15 saat","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"Pada tablet atau komputer riba dalam landskap, muat kamera untuk pratonton dan rakam.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Muat kamera apabila anda bersedia untuk merakam."},pt:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"Gire o dispositivo para a horizontal. A gravação com as mãos só funciona em paisagem em um tablet ou notebook.","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"A gravação com as mãos é para tablets e notebooks. A câmera, o rastreamento das mãos e o rastro de flores precisam de uma tela maior e mais processamento do que a maioria dos celulares oferece.","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"Paisagem obrigatória","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"Tablet ou notebook","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"Iniciando câmera…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"Tablet ou notebook · paisagem","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"Vídeo de criação pronto","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"Grave sua criação primeiro","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"Carregar câmera e rastreamento das mãos","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"Carregar câmera","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"Carregando câmera e rastreamento das mãos…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Iniciar gravação","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Gravar novamente","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Parar gravação","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Câmera pronta","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Carregue a câmera para visualizar","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Antes de gravar","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Abra em um tablet ou notebook","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"A gravação com as mãos usa sua câmera, rastreamento das mãos em tempo real e um rastro de flores ao vivo. Precisa de uma tela maior na horizontal e mais processamento do que a maioria dos celulares.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Gire o dispositivo (paisagem)","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Carregar câmera e rastreamento das mãos","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"Grave até 15 segundos","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"Em um tablet ou notebook na horizontal, carregue a câmera para visualizar e gravar.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Carregue a câmera quando estiver pronto para gravar."},th:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"หมุนอุปกรณ์เป็นแนวนอน การบันทึกด้วยมือใช้ได้เฉพาะแนวนอนบนแท็บเล็ตหรือแล็ปท็อป","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"การบันทึกด้วยมือสำหรับแท็บเล็ตและแล็ปท็อป กล้อง การติดตามมือ และรอยดอกไม้ต้องการหน้าจอที่ใหญ่กว่าและพลังประมวลผลมากกว่าโทรศัพท์ส่วนใหญ่","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"ต้องใช้แนวนอน","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"แท็บเล็ตหรือแล็ปท็อป","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"กำลังเปิดกล้อง…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"แท็บเล็ตหรือแล็ปท็อป · แนวนอน","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"วิดีโอการสร้างพร้อมแล้ว","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"บันทึกการสร้างของคุณก่อน","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"โหลดกล้องและการติดตามมือ","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"โหลดกล้อง","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"กำลังโหลดกล้องและการติดตามมือ…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"เริ่มบันทึก","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"บันทึกอีกครั้ง","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"หยุดบันทึก","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"กล้องพร้อม","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"โหลดกล้องเพื่อดูตัวอย่าง","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"ก่อนบันทึก","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"เปิดบนแท็บเล็ตหรือแล็ปท็อป","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"การบันทึกด้วยมือใช้กล้อง การติดตามมือแบบเรียลไทม์ และรอยดอกไม้สด ต้องการหน้าจอที่ใหญ่กว่าในแนวนอนและพลังประมวลผลมากกว่าโทรศัพท์ส่วนใหญ่","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"หมุนอุปกรณ์เป็นแนวนอน","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"โหลดกล้องและการติดตามมือ","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"บันทึกได้สูงสุด 15 วินาที","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"บนแท็บเล็ตหรือแล็ปท็อปในแนวนอน โหลดกล้องเพื่อดูตัวอย่างและบันทึก","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"โหลดกล้องเมื่อคุณพร้อมบันทึก"},tr:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"Cihazınızı yatay çevirin. El kaydı yalnızca tablet veya dizüstü bilgisayarda yatay modda çalışır.","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"El kaydı tablet ve dizüstü bilgisayarlar içindir. Kamera, el takibi ve çiçek izi, çoğu telefondan daha büyük bir ekran ve daha güçlü işlem gücü gerektirir.","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"Yatay gerekli","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"Tablet veya dizüstü","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"Kamera başlatılıyor…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"Tablet veya dizüstü · yatay","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"Oluşturma videosu hazır","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"Önce oluşturmanızı kaydedin","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"Kamera ve el takibini yükle","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"Kamerayı yükle","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"Kamera ve el takibi yükleniyor…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"Kaydı başlat","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"Tekrar kaydet","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"Kaydı durdur","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"Kamera hazır","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"Önizleme için kamerayı yükleyin","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"Kaydetmeden önce","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"Tablet veya dizüstü bilgisayarda açın","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"El kaydı kameranızı, gerçek zamanlı el takibini ve canlı çiçek izini kullanır. Yatay modda daha büyük bir ekran ve çoğu telefondan daha güçlü işlem gücü gerekir.","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"Cihazı yatay çevirin","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"Kamera ve el takibini yükle","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"En fazla 15 saniye kaydedin","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"Tablet veya dizüstü bilgisayarda yatay moddayken önizleme ve kayıt için kamerayı yükleyin.","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"Kayda hazır olduğunuzda kamerayı yükleyin."},zh:{"gift.creationIntro.portraitBlocked":"请将设备横过来。手部录制仅在平板或笔记本电脑的横屏模式下可用。","gift.creationIntro.phoneBlocked":"手部录制仅适用于平板和笔记本电脑。相机、手部追踪与花轨需要比大多数手机更大的屏幕和更强的处理能力。","gift.creationIntro.emptyPortrait":"需要横屏","gift.creationIntro.emptyPhone":"需要平板或笔记本","gift.creationIntro.emptyStarting":"正在启动相机…","gift.creationIntro.recordModeLabel":"平板或笔记本 · 横屏","gift.creationIntro.clipReadyLabel":"创作视频已就绪","gift.creationIntro.continueBlocked":"请先录制你的创作","gift.creationIntro.loadRecorder":"加载相机和手部追踪","gift.creationIntro.loadCamera":"加载相机","gift.creationIntro.loadingRecorder":"正在加载相机和手部追踪…","gift.creationIntro.startRecording":"开始录制","gift.creationIntro.recordAgain":"重新录制","gift.creationIntro.stopRecording":"停止录制","gift.creationIntro.cameraReady":"相机已就绪","gift.creationIntro.emptyLoadPrompt":"加载相机以预览","gift.creationIntro.requirementsEyebrow":"录制前","gift.creationIntro.requirementsTitle":"请在平板或笔记本电脑上打开","gift.creationIntro.requirementsLead":"手部录制会使用相机、实时手部追踪和实时花轨。它需要横屏下更大的屏幕，以及比大多数手机更强的处理能力。","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLandscape":"将设备横过来（横屏）","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepLoad":"加载相机和手部追踪","gift.creationIntro.requirementsStepRecord":"最多录制 15 秒","gift.creationIntro.studioPrepareHint":"在平板或笔记本横屏模式下，加载相机后即可预览并录制。","gift.creationIntro.emptyStudioHint":"准备好录制后再加载相机。"}};function Q(e){if(!e)return null;const t=e.toLowerCase().replace("_","-"),o=t.split("-")[0];return"zh"===o?"zh":O.has(t)?t:O.has(o)?o:null}z.forEach(e=>{Object.assign(H[e],W[e]),Object.assign(H[e],V[e])});const Y=function(){const e=new URLSearchParams(window.location.search),t=Q(e.get("lang")||e.get("locale"));if(t){try{window.localStorage.setItem(D,t)}catch{}return t}try{const e=Q(window.localStorage.getItem(D));if(e)return e}catch{}for(const o of navigator.languages??[na